Ninchat,is,a,persistent,chat,service,that,also,provides,live,video,meetings,and,filesharing,functions,The,chat,always,stays,on,even,when,the,user,is,not,online,and,maintains,an,unlimited,message,history,Users,can,have,multiple,channels,for,people,interest,groups,or,work,groups,each,with,its,own,web,address,and,message,history,Users,can,opt,to,receive,notifications,any,time,their,name,or,a,specified,word,is,mentioned,in,a,channel,Ninchat,users,can,hold,video,or,audio,meetings,with,up,to,speakers,and,unlimited,viewers,Ninchat,provides,a,REST,API,that,allows,developers,to,create,custom,clients,functionalities,or,bots,for,the,service